::Prowl::

Prowl nods. "Ready."

Launching himself from the tree, Prowl grabs Iron Raptor with his talons and 
flies up, flapping to get altitude.

He growls slightly. The wounds from Zenyak's dagger wern't helping much. His 
right shoulder felt like it was about to fall off.

Prowl keeps flying, thinking of all the un-maximal-like things he could do to 
Zenyak back at the Ark.
